'''Fik Meijer''' (born 12 August 1942) is a Dutch historian and author.

== Life ==

He studied classics and ancient history at Leiden University and graduated in 1973.

He is an emeritus professor of ancient history at the University of Amsterdam.<ref name="helanwenxue">{{cite web|url=http://www.helanwenxue.org/2011/speakers/en/fik-meijer.php|publisher=helanwenxue.org|title=Open Landscape, Open Book: Speakers: Fik Meijer|accessdate=2016-11-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.rd.nl/boeken/fik-meijer-schrijft-biografie-van-apostel-paulus-1.702441|title=Fik Meijer schrijft biografie van apostel Paulus|newspaper=RD.nl|access-date=2016-12-08}}</ref>

== Career ==

His books have been translated into multiple languages.<ref name="letterenfonds">{{cite web|url=http://www.letterenfonds.nl/en/author/7/fik-meijer|publisher=letterenfonds.nl|title=Author - Fik Meijer - Letterenfonds|accessdate=2016-11-14}}</ref>

His book about Gladiators was very well researched and has consistently received good reviews.<ref name="andrewfullercenter">{{cite web|url=http://www.andrewfullercenter.org/blog/2008/03/book-review-of-fik-meijer-the-gladiators/|publisher=andrewfullercenter.org|title=Andrew Fuller Center &raquo; Book Review of Fik Meijer, the Gladiators|accessdate=2016-11-14}}</ref><ref name="goodreads">{{cite web|url=http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/127934.The_Gladiators|publisher=goodreads.com|title=The Gladiators: History's Most Deadly Sport by Fik Meijer — Reviews, Discussion, Bookclubs, Lists|accessdate=2016-11-14}}</ref><ref name="goodreads2">{{cite web|url=http://www.goodreads.com/author/show/73410.Fik_Meijer|publisher=goodreads.com|title=Fik Meijer (Author of The Gladiators)|accessdate=2016-11-14}}</ref><ref name="amazon2">{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/Gladiators-Historys-Most-Deadly-Sport/dp/0312364024|publisher=web.archive.org|title=The Gladiators: History&#39;s Most Deadly Sport: Fik Meijer: 9780312364021: Amazon.com: Books|accessdate=2016-11-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114235309/https://www.amazon.com/Gladiators-Historys-Most-Deadly-Sport/dp/0312364024|archivedate=2016-11-14|df=}}</ref>

