== Personal life ==
From some time in the 1930s until her death Freeman lived with her companion Dr Liliane Marie Catherine Clopet (1901-1987), a GP and author, at Lark's Rise, a house in [[St Mellons]] (now a district of [[Cardiff]]).<ref name=":0" />

