|-
| 1860 || || [[Benjamin Tyler Henry]] invents the [[Henry rifle]], the first reliable [[repeating rifle]].{{sfn|Willbanks|2004|p=17}}
|-
| 1861 || || [[Richard Jordan Gatling]] invents the [[Gatling gun]], capable of firing 200 gunpowder cartridges in a minute.{{sfn|Chase|2003|p=202}}
|-
| rowspan="2" valign="top" | 1862 || || The [[Qing dynasty]] starts production of [[percussion caps]] for [[rifles]].{{sfn|Needham|1986|p=467}}
|-
